videos.description: Alex Barnes makes a great  38-yard run to put Kansas State in the red zone.
videos.headline: Wildcats' Barnes makes impressive run

videos.description: Wildcats' Jesse Ertz throws the ball deep to Isaiah Zuber in the corner of the end zone for a 16-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Kansas on the board first with TD

videos.description: Kansas State's Cre Moore is disqualified from the game for a helmet-to-helmet hit in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Wildcats' Moore is ejected from game for targeting

videos.description: Wildcats' D.J. Reed returns the punt but fumbles the ball and it's recovered by Baylor's Marques Jones.
videos.headline: Kansas fumble leads to turnover

videos.description: Modern Family actor Eric Stonestreet takes a walk down memory lane and shares his favorite memories as a Kansas State student.
videos.headline: Modern Family actor shares his K-State memories

videos.description: Kansas State's Winston Dimel pushes through the defense for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Dimel runs up the middle for Wildcat TD

videos.description: Bill Snyder says the Wildcats need to be more consistent in the second half and breaks down K-State's offense.
videos.headline: Snyder discusses how Wildcats need to be more consistent

videos.description: Baylor's head coach Matt Rhule discusses how they need to eliminate penalties to get big plays on offense.
videos.headline: Baylor's head coach Rhule discusses penalties

videos.description: Baylor's Connor Martin fakes the punt and runs for 16 yards but gets drilled by Wildcats' AJ Parker.
videos.headline: Baylor punter pays the price for 1st down run

videos.description: Baylor snaps the ball over the quarterback's head and the ball is recovered by Wildcats' Kyle Ball.
videos.headline: Baylor loses the ball on terrible snap

videos.description: Jesse Ertz runs for 15 yards for a Wildcats' touchdown.
videos.headline: Kansas State QB with 15-yard TD

videos.description: Bears' Denzel Mims out runs two Wildcats for an impressive touchdown run.
videos.headline: Baylor's Mims runs for 70-yards TD

videos.description: Baylor's quarterback Zach Smith throws an interception late in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Kansas State ices game with interception

videos.description: Despite winning 33-20, Bill Snyder is not happy with the Wildcats' defense performance in the second half.
videos.headline: Snyder not happy with defense in second half

videos.description: ESPN's Anthony Becht says if K-State can fix their wide receivers inconsistency then they will be dangerous in the Big 12.
videos.headline: Anthony Becht talks about K-States WR

videos.description: Anthony Becht and Beth Mowins discusses Baylor's tough road ahead and how K-State offense revolves around their quarterback Jesse Ertz.
videos.headline: Baylor has a tough road ahead
